##################################################### Terraform basics #################################################################
What is Terraform?
Terraform is a infrastructure as a code tool.It is used to create infrastructure. You can create multiple infrastructure and manage infrastructure at a time by using Terraform.

Advantages of Using Terraform:-

a) Terraform can manage infrastructure on multiple cloud platforms.
b) The human readable configuration language helps you write infrastructure code quickly.
c) Terraform state allow you to track resource changes throughout your deployment.

Note:- You can manage any cloud Provider (AWS, Azure, GCP) by using Terraform at same time.
